{
  "stem": "18626.10",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 356.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was all the time because it was so suspense what you saw and what people, they're telling their stories-- that I thought my stories was big.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My story was-- comparing with other stories, was very little, minor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The courtroom was a very big room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that was the entertainment hall for the SS, I think.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when the Americans took over, they made it a courtroom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a tremendous, big hall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, as a mechanic, I would say it must have been [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] about 150 feet or 200 feet by 500 feet, long hall with-- all set up like regular big courtrooms, you know, like for-- almost like a Nuremberg Trial.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were sitting right close, like-- almost like in the movie, we were sitting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The matter of fact, on the trial was even the relatives from the criminals who got sentence, all from the 40 criminals who were sentenced-- or going to be sentenced.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Their wives, their brothers, or relatives-- they're in the courtroom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because not far from me on the third seat, they are sitting, [LAUGHS] by coincidence-- the commandant that-- Johann Kirsch from my camp, his wife, and some relatives, maybe sons or something like that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I heard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While we were brought in, the MP guided us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Go in that row.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Go in that row.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, like, like a usher, almost, in the movies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was not far, you know, from the family, like, two seats.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was hearing what she was talking in German to her-- to her son, or somebody.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was holding her hand like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My poor, my, my [GERMAN] Johann.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My [GERMAN] Johann, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
